- Navigators metaphorically refer to users exploring the economic data; 
- Economic landscapes metaphorically represent the GDP data for different countries; 
- Hidden valleys metaphorically refer to the lowest GDPs recorded; 
- Towering peaks metaphorically refer to the highest GDPs recorded; 
- Rocky paths metaphorically refer to the average GDPs recorded.

sql:
SELECT user_name AS name FROM users WHERE role = 'analyst'
UNION
SELECT country_name AS name FROM countries WHERE population > 100000000;
